title: Bioobchod.cz - I.P.Pavlova
description: Vegetarian and vegan shop offering a wide range of products including chilled food, vegan cheese, vegan sausages, vegan "fish sticks", fresh pressed juices, baked products, salads, fresh fruits and vegetables, teas, natural cosmetics, ecological cleansing products, and eco children toys. Originally vegan but added eggs and dairy to its stock in summer 2013.
